Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:44.14,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, che bello, che bello!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:47.22,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non fare così. Calmati ora.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:47.50,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, no, Guarda, guarda!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:52.21,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Smettila di correre in giro, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:54.19,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Torna subito qui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:32.39,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Oh, my God! - Oh, mio Dio!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:33.93,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{ I'm very sorry! - Mi dispiace tanto!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:35.71,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Are you all right? Are you injuried? - Stai bene? Sei ferito?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:38.17,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{I've been ..... for two days. - Sono stata su un aeroplano per  due giorni}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:40.42,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{So I'm look around\Nwith ugly appetite.  - Perciò mi guardavo attorno con una fame terribile.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:41.19,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Watch me man.  - Guardami ragazzo.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:41.32,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ah... Asp... Aspetti...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:43.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Did you hit the head? \NDo you have any pain?  - Hai battuto la testa?\N Ti fa male da qualche parte?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:45.06,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{.............}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.64,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{I'll have to take \Nthe responsibility. - Devo assumermene la responsabilità.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:48.12,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Huh?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:53.81,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sembri stare bene, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.29,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Gen-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.05,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ci vediamo, bel ragazzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:07.50,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,È lei Hiraga Gen-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:11.00,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sono venuta a prenderla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:15.79,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, giusto. Sei il mio passaggio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:17.54,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sì.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:18.48,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:23.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Poco fa, qualcuno mi ha\N urtato e sono caduto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.19,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Prendo i bagagli.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.04,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.88,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Su, andiamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:49.42,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Io sono la domestica\N della residenza, Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.73,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Come conoscevi il mio viso?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.94,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ho visto una sua fotografia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:54.80,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.99,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Però, quando ho saputo\N che c'era una domestica
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.25,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,pensavo fosse più vecchia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:04.10,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Se pensa che sia più\N vecchia, ha ragione.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.55,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Oh, davvero?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:06.84,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Circa 19?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.60,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ne ho 416.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:15.98,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Stai bene?\NForse dovrei portarle io.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:17.78,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sto bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:20.45,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Io sono una domestica.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:26.51,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Mia nonna... che tipo è?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:31.81,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,No, è che io... \Nnon l'ho mai incontrata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:34.10,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,È molto buona.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.77,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Beh, sono certo che lo sia, ma
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:42.78,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,prima della morte della\N mamma, nemmeno sapevo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.50,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,che la nonna esistesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.03,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non si preoccupi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.58,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,La signora la conosce.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:51.70,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Di questo sono certo, però...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:03.32,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Eh, che c'è?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.75,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,No, ecco...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:07.53,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Mi scusi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:39.88,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Alberi di ciliegio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.13,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sono sacri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.80,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Su, ecco che arriva Sakura-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Le ho portato Gen-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.47,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Oh, sei cresciuto tanto, Gen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:09.77,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Davvero, quanto tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:14.73,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,In ogni caso dubito\N che tu mi ricordi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:21.17,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,L'ultima volta che ti ho visto è\N stata la primavera di 12 anni fa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.95,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Devi essere arrabbiato con me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:31.68,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Per non averti mandato nemmeno una lettera
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:35.50,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,e non essere andata al funerale di Sakurako.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.54,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Perdonami, ti prego.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:42.91,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Nelle mie condizioni non posso stare molto fuori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.79,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,È successo in un incidente,\N molto tempo fa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:50.89,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Indosso una maschera\N a causa di quello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:55.32,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Io non voglio che ci\N siano rancori tra noi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.48,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Per la tomba della Mamma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:52.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Nonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.67,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Grazie di avermi accolto, Nonna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.28,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.94,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:07.67,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:16.36,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Gen, da oggi questa è casa tua.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.90,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Se ti serve qualcosa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.28,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,chiedi pure a Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.40,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Ho affidato a lei l'incarico
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.76,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,di occuparsi di ogni tua necessità.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.31,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Beth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:30.98,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Beatrice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:32.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sì?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:36.06,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Mostra a Gen la sua stanza.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.14,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sì.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.47,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Da domani
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.12,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,puoi cominciare a \Nfrequentare il mio college.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.22,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Ho già dato le disposizioni.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.39,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sicuramente sarà stanco\N dopo quel lungo viaggio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.87,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Devo prepararle un bagno?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.95,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Oppure devo prepararle\N subito il letto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.06,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Va bene così.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:08:59.93,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Allora...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:50.14,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Ho sempre pensato che fosse un sogno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.25,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Quei ciliegi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.96,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,In realtà devo già essere stato qui.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:09:59.13,Internal,,0,0,0,,Però...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:00.60,Internal,,0,0,0,,quella...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:01.98,Internal,,0,0,0,,chi è?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.12,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Sono terribilmente spiacente, Gen-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:34.76,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Betj, non è colpa tua\N se ho dormito troppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:38.11,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,E poi, non chiamarmi Gen-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:41.99,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Però Gen-sama è il discendente diretto della Signora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:44.09,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Davvero Gen-sama devo chiamarla Gen-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:44.47,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sto uscendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:49.08,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Abbia una buona giornata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.68,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Il vecchio edificio, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.78,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Wha...?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:32.99,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Sensei, ora...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.17,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,mi perdoni
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.05,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,per favore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:01.38,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Così non va bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:04.18,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non devi fare tanto rumore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:12.89,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Sensei..?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:15.48,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Che c'è?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.40,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Per favore..!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:19.76,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:23.20,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,mi tocchi con le sue dita per favore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:25.62,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Qui?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:27.77,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,No, non lì.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:29.61,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Allora, qui?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.53,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Nemmeno lì.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.40,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Se non sei più precisa
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:38.66,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,la Sensei come può saperlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:41.73,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ecco...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:43.94,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Come? Non ti sento.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.96,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.29,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Che devo fare con te?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.27,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Allora, se ti mettessi sulle ginocchia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:27.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sensei... la prego, basta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.56,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non mi stuzzichi più, per favore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.83,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sei tu il nuovo studente?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:49.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ti stavo cercando.\N La Sensei mi ha detto di trovarti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.93,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Cos'è quell'aspetto trasandato?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:54.59,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Il codice di abbigliamento\N nel manuale dello studente
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:55.97,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,non l'hai letto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.84,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Guarda, Ayumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.93,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Che succede?\N Non dovresti essere a lezione?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.78,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Stavo cercando il nuovo studente trasferito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:11.22,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Allora, tu sei il nipote della preside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:16.04,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,La tua cravatta è un po' storta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:19.54,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ito-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:23.10,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Io devo mostrare la scuola a questo studente.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:30.73,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:31.96,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Aspetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:37.21,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,L'hai visto, vero?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:39.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Lo stavano facendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,No... beh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.25,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Quella... è mia madre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:48.18,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{What...?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:14:59.89,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Permesso...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.08,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sakurako-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:03.27,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,C'è voluto davvero un po'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:05.50,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Si era perso?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:09.07,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Chissà? Penso che abbia \Ntrovato diverse cose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.25,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Avanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:49.20,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sono il tuo insegnante di\N orientamento per oggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:51.00,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sono Sakurako Rokuhira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.27,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Che succede?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:09.19,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,F-Fuori c'erano i ciliegi in fiore ed era bellissimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:09.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.61,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Io l'ho già vista!\N L'ho vista in un sogno!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:27.77,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sei in ritardo il primo giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:31.06,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sarai uno studente problematico?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:33.72,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, no... Non è così.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.15,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Hiraga Gen-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:38.54,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,per il tuo prossimo anno...\Nimpegnati, eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:48.68,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Oggi abbiamo un nuovo studente.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:52.72,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Il suo nome è Hiraga Gen\Ne spero che andrete d'accordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:55.57,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Inoltre è il nipote della Preside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:58.09,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Ragazzi, prendetevene cura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:01.34,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Rappresentante!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:04.91,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Posso farti una domanda strana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:07.60,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Quella Rokuhira-sensei, che tipo è?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:12.25,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Sai la sua età?\N O da quanto è in questa scuola?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.70,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Perché non glielo chiedi tu stesso?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:17.12,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tu sei il nipote della\N Preside, dopo tutto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.18,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, giusto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:20.91,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Hai ragione.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.89,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,C'è molta competizione\N per Sakurako-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:24.80,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.76,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tutti i ragazzi le vanno dietro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:28.79,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Really...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:34.42,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,E non sono solo... \Ni ragazzi ad andarle dietro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:18.08,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Sono a casa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:19.64,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ma..?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.04,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non c'è nessuno in casa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:24.02,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Beth-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:30.32,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non sembra molto affidabile\N per essere una domestica.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:35.20,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Diamine..!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:39.45,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Beth-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:44.81,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Che succede? Riprenditi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:58.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Beth-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.14,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ora, chiamo un dottore...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:02.53,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stia indietro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:06.64,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Io, tra poco... starò bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.65,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Per favore, può chiudere le tende?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.05,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Le tende?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:12.46,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Perché?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:26.14,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Beth..?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:30.03,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Io... non sono normale.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:36.15,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Perciò, non voglio creare altri\N problemi a Gen-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:38.49,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Stia indietro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:40.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.96,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Di cosa... si tratta?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:49.30,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:19:59.79,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Beth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:01.56,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,La prego...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:05.46,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Gen-sama... posso avere la sua Aqua Permanence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.42,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Aqua... che cosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:13.73,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Aqua Permanence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:18.88,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Che cos'è?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:21.81,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Gen-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:24.87,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Hei, hei..?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:26.04,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Mi scusi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:27.83,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Mi scusi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:30.63,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Che stai facendo?! Fermati!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:31.35,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Fermat..!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:33.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Gen-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:35.99,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Hei! Che stai..?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.32,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Signora, mi perdoni.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:11.76,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Fermati...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:14.58,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Fer... mati...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:36.84,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non guardare!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:52.53,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Davvero...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:54.88,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,è dorato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:21:59.12,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Gen-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:01.36,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,L'hai visto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:04.34,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Io... sono strano.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:07.40,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Penso di essere malato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:13.67,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Gen-sama, questo è...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:22.02,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Mi dispiace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:50.48,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Gen-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:52.25,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Come?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:53.77,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Perché...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:56.23,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,è successo questo, ora?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:02.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non ho mai pianto prima.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:05.65,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Eravamo solo io e mia madre.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:07.80,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ma anche quando è morta...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:10.28,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,non ho pensato a questo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:14.62,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Io... ho solo pensato che\N sarei stato solo da allora.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.88,0:23:17.81,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Avevo più paura di quello.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.74,0:23:22.17,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Per la mamma... \Nnon ho potuto fare nulla.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:24.68,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,La capisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.31,0:23:27.82,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Anche io ero sempre sola.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.97,0:23:30.27,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non sia triste.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.61,0:24:17.67,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Beth, tu... a questo...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.99,0:24:19.95,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,sei abituata?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.37,0:24:23.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,È così.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.87,0:24:25.89,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Anche se sono passati 112 anni.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.52,0:24:27.18,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.37,0:24:36.00,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Gen-sama, si rilassi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.53,0:24:38.59,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Lasci che mi occupi io del resto.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.66,0:24:55.46,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Quando lo compresi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.12,0:24:57.40,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,ero sola.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.22,0:25:01.40,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Da quando sono nata.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.89,0:25:04.81,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Finché la Signora mi ha trovato
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.26,0:25:07.24,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,e mi ha portato in questa casa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.64,0:25:15.62,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Gen-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.64,0:25:25.30,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Non soffrivi la solitudine?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.14,0:25:26.76,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Sì.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.73,0:25:30.17,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Però, ora sto bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.95,0:25:37.84,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Perché ora non sono più sola.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.50,0:25:39.25,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Beth...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.12,0:25:56.14,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Quella Aqua di cui parlavi prima, che cos'è?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.61,0:26:00.66,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Beth, tu sai qualcosa\N della mia condizione?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.00,0:26:02.95,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Quello...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.45,0:26:05.69,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Quando sarà il momento...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.26,0:26:09.52,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,la Signora sicuramente glielo spiegherà.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.17,0:26:12.28,Internal,,0,0,0,,La nonna?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.62,0:26:29.16,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Passi una buona giornata!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.62,0:26:44.44,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Scusami...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.24,0:26:48.98,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Lei... è quella donna...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.17,0:26:50.33,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Hei, dolcezza...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.60,0:26:52.19,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Hai un momento?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.16,0:26:56.79,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Aspetta! Una donna ti \Nsta chiedendo di uscire!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.21,0:27:00.04,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Beh, non posso biasimarti.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.33,0:27:02.72,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Di certo ne hai avuto a\N sufficienza la scorsa notte, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.21,0:27:04.76,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Aqua Permanence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.68,0:27:06.15,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{What?}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.75,0:27:11.69,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Allora? Vieni?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.10,0:27:20.07,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Di cosa vuole parlare comunque?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.33,0:27:21.85,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tu, chi sei?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.00,0:27:25.81,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Cerca di rilassarti.\N Ci siamo solo noi qui.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.88,0:27:27.45,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Stai giocando con me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.51,0:27:31.77,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Te lo dirò.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.21,0:27:34.99,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Lo sperma dorato è il segno\N dell'eterna giovinezza.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.95,0:27:37.46,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Eterna giovinezza?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.81,0:27:38.47,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Già.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.20,0:27:46.82,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Mi piacerebbe conoscerti molto meglio.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.86,0:29:12.86,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,
